embed.description: Hey, welcome to a brand new video, this time having a look at Kayn, The Shadow Reaper. The video will show you the abilities and my very first attempt in using Kayn in a public match! If you like my attempt at explaining a champions kit (or not), please give the video a like and sub regardless as all the help is appreciated!
